---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="RAG vs Fine-Tuning vs Few-Shot">
    <div class="main-wrapper">
        <div class="background-glow"></div>

        <div class="container">
            <header class="header animate-fade-in">
                <h1 class="title">
                    Guía Rápida: <br />
                    <span class="text-gradient"
                        >RAG vs Fine-Tuning vs Few-Shot</span
                    >
                </h1>
                <p class="subtitle">
                    Entiende las diferencias clave entre estas tres técnicas
                    para mejorar el rendimiento de tus modelos de IA de forma
                    práctica y sencilla.
                </p>

                <div class="actions">
                    <a class="button-primary" href="#comparison">
                        Ver Comparación
                    </a>
                </div>
            </header>

            <section class="grid">
                <div
                    class="card intro-card animate-slide-up"
                    style="--delay: 100ms"
                >
                    <div class="card-icon"></div>
                    <h3>¿Por Qué Elegir Una U Otra?</h3>
                    <p>
                        Cada técnica resuelve problemas diferentes. RAG para
                        información actualizada, Fine-Tuning para comportamiento
                        especializado, y Few-Shot para ajustes rápidos.
                    </p>
                    <div class="features-list">
                        <span class="feature-tag">RAG → Datos Actuales</span>
                        <span class="feature-tag"
                            >Fine-Tuning → Comportamiento</span
                        >
                        <span class="feature-tag">Few-Shot → Rápido</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 200ms">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3>RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-explanation">
                        <p>
                            <strong>En simple:</strong> Como darle un libro de referencia
                            al modelo para que consulte mientras responde.
                        </p>

                        <div class="analogy">
                            <strong>Analogía:</strong> Un estudiante que tiene permitido
                            usar sus apuntes durante el examen.
                        </div>

                        <div class="terminal-window">
                            <div class="terminal-header">
                                <span class="dot red"></span>
                                <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                                <span class="dot green"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="code-content">
                                <span class="code-comment"
                                    ># Flujo básico de RAG</span
                                ><br />
                                1. Usuario hace una pregunta<br />
                                2. Sistema busca en base de datos<br />
                                3. Encuentra información relevante<br />
                                4. Modelo responde usando esa info<br />
                                5. <span class="code-string"
                                    >→ Respuesta actualizada y precisa</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 300ms">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3>Fine-Tuning</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-explanation">
                        <p>
                            <strong>En simple:</strong> Re-entrenar el modelo para
                            que se especialice en una tarea específica.
                        </p>

                        <div class="analogy">
                            <strong>Analogía:</strong> Entrenar a un chef general
                            para que se convierta en experto en sushi.
                        </div>

                        <div class="terminal-window">
                            <div class="terminal-header">
                                <span class="dot red"></span>
                                <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                                <span class="dot green"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="code-content">
                                <span class="code-comment"
                                    ># Proceso de Fine-Tuning</span
                                ><br />
                                Modelo base + Datos especializados<br />
                                ↓<br />
                                Entrenamiento adicional<br />
                                ↓<br />
                                <span class="code-string"
                                    >Modelo especializado</span
                                ><br /><br />

                                <span class="code-comment"
                                    ># Ejemplo: Entrenar para</span
                                ><br />
                                - Jerga legal médica<br />
                                - Tono de marca específico<br />
                                - Formato de respuestas único
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 400ms">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3>Few-Shot Learning</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="concept-explanation">
                        <p>
                            <strong>En simple:</strong> Darle algunos ejemplos al
                            modelo en el prompt para que aprenda el patrón.
                        </p>

                        <div class="analogy">
                            <strong>Analogía:</strong> Mostrarle a alguien 3 fotos
                            de gatos para que aprenda a reconocer gatos.
                        </div>

                        <div class="terminal-window">
                            <div class="terminal-header">
                                <span class="dot red"></span>
                                <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                                <span class="dot green"></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="code-content">
                                <span class="code-comment"
                                    ># Ejemplo de Few-Shot</span
                                ><br />
                                <span class="code-string"
                                    >"Traduce al español:"</span
                                ><br />
                                Hello → Hola<br />
                                Goodbye → Adiós<br />
                                Thank you → Gracias<br />
                                How are you? → <span class="code-comment"
                                    ># El modelo completa</span
                                >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 500ms">
                    <h3>Velocidad vs Efectividad</h3>
                    <div class="comparison-bars">
                        <div class="bar-item">
                            <span>Few-Shot</span>
                            <div class="bar-container">
                                <div class="bar speed" style="width: 95%"></div>
                                <div
                                    class="bar effectiveness"
                                    style="width: 60%"
                                >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bar-item">
                            <span>RAG</span>
                            <div class="bar-container">
                                <div class="bar speed" style="width: 70%"></div>
                                <div
                                    class="bar effectiveness"
                                    style="width: 85%"
                                >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bar-item">
                            <span>Fine-Tuning</span>
                            <div class="bar-container">
                                <div class="bar speed" style="width: 30%"></div>
                                <div
                                    class="bar effectiveness"
                                    style="width: 95%"
                                >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bar-legend">
                        <div class="legend-item">
                            <div class="legend-color speed"></div>
                            <span>Velocidad de implementación</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="legend-item">
                            <div class="legend-color effectiveness"></div>
                            <span>Efectividad en tarea específica</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 600ms">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3>Casos de Uso Prácticos</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="use-cases">
                        <div class="use-case-item">
                            <strong>RAG</strong>
                            <span
                                >Chatbot que responde sobre documentos
                                actualizados</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="use-case-item">
                            <strong>Fine-Tuning</strong>
                            <span
                                >Asistente médico con terminología especializada</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div class="use-case-item">
                            <strong>Few-Shot</strong>
                            <span
                                >Clasificar emails rápidamente con ejemplos</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    id="comparison"
                    class="card full-width animate-slide-up"
                    style="--delay: 700ms"
                >
                    <h3>Comparación Directa</h3>
                    <div class="comparison-table">
                        <div class="table-header">
                            <div class="table-cell">Característica</div>
                            <div class="table-cell">Few-Shot</div>
                            <div class="table-cell">RAG</div>
                            <div class="table-cell">Fine-Tuning</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell">Tiempo setup</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">
                                Minutos
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-yellow">Horas</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-red">
                                Días/Semanas
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell">Costo</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">
                                Muy bajo
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-yellow">
                                Moderado
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-red">Alto</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell">Flexibilidad</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">Alta</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">Alta</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-red">Baja</div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell">Precisión</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-yellow">
                                Moderada
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">Alta</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">
                                Muy alta
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="table-row">
                            <div class="table-cell">Datos necesarios</div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-green">
                                3-10 ejemplos
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-yellow">
                                Base de datos
                            </div>
                            <div class="table-cell highlight-red">
                                Miles de ejemplos
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 800ms">
                    <h3>¿Cuándo Usar Cada Una?</h3>
                    <div class="decision-flow">
                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-question">
                                ¿Necesitas información actualizada
                                frecuentemente?
                            </div>
                            <div class="flow-answer">
                                <span class="answer-yes">Sí →</span>
                                <strong class="technique">RAG</strong>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-question">
                                ¿Es un problema muy específico que requiere
                                comportamiento único?
                            </div>
                            <div class="flow-answer">
                                <span class="answer-yes">Sí →</span>
                                <strong class="technique">Fine-Tuning</strong>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flow-step">
                            <div class="flow-question">
                                ¿Necesitas una solución rápida para probar una
                                idea?
                            </div>
                            <div class="flow-answer">
                                <span class="answer-yes">Sí →</span>
                                <strong class="technique">Few-Shot</strong>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card animate-slide-up" style="--delay: 900ms">
                    <h3>Ejemplo Rápido: Few-Shot</h3>
                    <div class="terminal-window">
                        <div class="terminal-header">
                            <span class="dot red"></span>
                            <span class="dot yellow"></span>
                            <span class="dot green"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="code-content">
                            <span class="code-comment"
                                ># Clasificar sentimientos con ejemplos</span
                            ><br />
                            <span class="code-string"
                                >"Clasifica el sentimiento:"</span
                            ><br />
                            "Me encanta este producto" → POSITIVO<br />
                            "Odio cuando esto pasa" → NEGATIVO<br />
                            "El servicio fue regular" → NEUTRAL<br />
                            "No está mal para el precio" → <span
                                class="code-comment"># El modelo completa</span
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    :root {
        --bg-dark: #09090b;
        --bg-card: #18181b;
        --bg-card-hover: #27272a;
        --border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        --text-main: #f4f4f5;
        --text-muted: #a1a1aa;
        --gradient-title: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-green) 0%, var(--accent-cyan) 100%);
        --accent-purple: #8b5cf6;
        --accent-cyan: #06b6d4;
    }

    .main-wrapper {
        background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        min-height: 100vh;
        color: var(--text-main);
        font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
        position: relative;
        overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .background-glow {
        position: absolute;
        top: -20%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 60vw;
        height: 60vh;
        background: radial-gradient(
            circle,
            rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15) 0%,
            transparent 70%
        );
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 60px 20px;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
    }

    /* Header Styles */
    .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .text-gradient {
        background: var(--gradient-title);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .subtitle {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 32px auto;
    }

    .button-primary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        background: var(--text-main);
        color: var(--bg-dark);
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button-primary:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Grid and Cards */
    .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        gap: 24px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .card {
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card:hover {
        border-color: var(--accent-purple);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .card.full-width {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: var(--text-main);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .intro-card p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .features-list {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 8px;
    }

    .feature-tag {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 6px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Concept Explanation */
    .concept-explanation {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .analogy {
        background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-purple);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Comparison Bars */
    .comparison-bars {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .bar-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .bar-item span {
        min-width: 80px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-main);
    }

    .bar-container {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        gap: 4px;
        height: 20px;
    }

    .bar {
        border-radius: 4px;
        transition: width 0.3s ease;
    }

    .bar.speed {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10b981, #34d399);
    }

    .bar.effectiveness {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #60a5fa);
    }

    .bar-legend {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 12px;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .legend-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .legend-color {
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .legend-color.speed {
        background: var(--accent-green);
    }

    .legend-color.effectiveness {
        background: var(--accent-blue);
    }

    /* Use Cases */
    .use-cases {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
    }

    .use-case-item {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 4px;
        padding-bottom: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .use-case-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
    }

    .use-case-item strong {
        color: var(--accent-cyan);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .use-case-item span {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    /* Comparison Table */
    .comparison-table {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    .table-header {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .table-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .table-cell {
        padding: 12px 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .highlight-green {
        background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-green);
    }

    .highlight-yellow {
        background: rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-orange);
    }

    .highlight-red {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
        color: #f87171;
    }

    /* Decision Flow */
    .decision-flow {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .flow-step {
        padding: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        border-radius: 8px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-cyan);
    }

    .flow-question {
        color: var(--text-main);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .flow-answer {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .answer-yes {
        color: var(--accent-green);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .technique {
        color: var(--accent-purple);
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Terminal Window Styling */
    .terminal-window {
        background: #0f1115;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-top: auto;
    }

    .terminal-header {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
        padding: 8px 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 6px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .dot {
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .dot.red {
        background: #ef4444;
    }
    .dot.yellow {
        background: var(--accent-orange);
    }
    .dot.green {
        background: var(--accent-green);
    }

    .code-content {
        padding: 16px;
        font-family: "Fira Code", "Menlo", monospace;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        overflow-x: auto;
        color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* Syntax Highlighting */
    .code-comment {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-style: italic;
    }
    .code-string {
        color: var(--accent-green);
    }

    /* Footer Grid */
    .footer-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 24px;
    }

    .warning-box,
    .tip-box {
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .warning-box {
        background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        color: #fca5a5;
    }

    .tip-box {
        background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
        color: #93c5fd;
    }

    .warning-box ul,
    .tip-box ul {
        margin: 8px 0 0 20px;
        padding: 0;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
        }
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .animate-slide-up {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out forwards;
        animation-delay: var(--delay, 0ms);
    }

    /* Responsive */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .footer-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .table-header,
        .table-row {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
        .bar-item {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        .bar-legend {
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 8px;
        }
    }
</style>
